		<text oae-label="Text" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="15">
			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>     Hi, Paulina.  I <blank word="'m going to get;am going to get"/> (<i>get</i>) married next week.      
<b>B:</b>     That's great!  What <blank word="'s;is" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>be</i>) your future husband's name?
<b>A:</b>     Mike Waters.
<b>B:</b>     Where <blank word="did" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="meet"/> (<i>meet</i>)?
<b>A:</b>     At Corning University in New Hampshire.  We <blank word="studied"/> (<i>study</i>) business there.  We <blank word="graduated"/> (<i>graduate</i>) last year.  
<b>B:</b>     Where <blank word="did" blanksize="Small"/> Mike <blank word="grow up"/> (<i>grow up</i>)?
<b>A:</b>     He <blank word="grew up"/> (<i>grow up</i>) in New Hampshire.  Actually, he <blank word="was born"/> (<i>be born</i>) there, too.
<b>B:</b>     &nbsp;<blank word="Are" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="going to move"/> (<i>move</i>) to New Hampshire, or <blank word="are" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="going to live"/>  (<i>live</i>) here in Chicago?
<b>A:</b>     We <blank word="'re going to live;are going to live"/> (<i>live</i>) in Chicago.  Mike <blank word="got"/> (<i>get</i>) a job last month as a manager at a bank.  
<b>B:</b>     What about you? What <blank word="are" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="going to do"/> (<i>do</i>)?
<b>A:</b>     I <blank word="'m going to work;am going to work"/> (<i>work</i>) at the art museum three days a week.
<b>B:</b>     Sounds great.  I'd like to meet Mike.  Any plans for dinner tonight?
<b>A:</b>     Actually, we <blank word="'re;are" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>be</i>) too busy now.  But definitely next month.]]>
